title: My pixel 5 needs updating but in settings it states that its already is up to date. Please help
content: I believe my pixel 5 has an update stuck in background which making it always heating as it seems that CPU is always running full while it actually not, i tried to update through settings but no chance there as it states that it is up to date while I received a notification message that I was late for an update but wasn't able to click on it.
